    • withCellPhone

      public B withCellPhone(String cellPhone)
      Sets up the cell phone value and sets it as the primary phone. If this method is invoked in addition to ContactBuilder.withWorkPhone(String) the last method invoked takes precidence (e.g. withWorkPhone("X").withHomePhone("Y") yeilds the home phone as the primary phone. Note: this field only applies to a Person contact and may produce undesired effects for a company contact
      Returns:
      ContactBuilder
